---
---

<section class="relative py-12 md:py-20 text-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Glowing Background Orbs -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-neon-cyan/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none animate-pulse-glow"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-neon-purple/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
    <!-- Live Status Pill -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-dark-card/90 border border-neon-cyan/30 shadow-lg shadow-neon-cyan/5 text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-300 backdrop-blur-md">
      <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-neon-cyan opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-neon-cyan"></span>
      </span>
      <span>تحديث تلقائي صباحي يومياً • بدون هلوسة أو تزييف</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Title -->
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold font-heading text-white leading-tight">
      عالم الذكاء الاصطناعي بين يديك
      <br />
      <span class="gradient-text">ملخّص وموثّق بالعربية</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
      نستخلص لك أهم مستجدات كبرى الشركات والمختبرات العالمية مثل OpenAI و Google DeepMind و Anthropic مع ملخصات دقيقة ودليل أدوات شمول مجاناً بالكامل.
    </p>

    <!-- Action Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 pt-4">
      <a
        href="/news"
        class="px-7 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-neon-cyan via-blue-500 to-neon-purple text-black font-bold text-base hover:opacity-95 shadow-xl shadow-neon-cyan/20 hover:shadow-neon-cyan/40 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        أخبار اليوم
      </a>

      <a
        href="/tools"
        class="px-7 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-dark-card/90 text-white font-semibold text-base border border-dark-border hover:border-neon-cyan/40 hover:bg-dark-hover transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        دليل الأدوات الجديد
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Bar -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-10 border-t border-dark-border/40 text-xs sm:text-sm text-gray-400">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neon-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
        <span>مصداقية تامة مع المصادر</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neon-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
        </svg>
        <span>بحث سريع فوري</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neon-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
        </svg>
        <span>نشرة بريدية صباحية</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neon-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        <span>مجاني 100% للأبد</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
